### 2. CSS (`style.css`)

This provides basic styling, ensuring responsiveness for the navigation and a clean layout.

```css
/* Basic Reset */
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    font-family: sans-serif;
}

body {
    background-color: #f4f4f9;
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

header {
    background-color: #1a1a2e;
    color: white;
    padding: 1rem 5%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
}

.logo {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
}

/* Navigation Styling */
#navbar a {
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-left: 20px;
    transition: color 0.3s;
}

#navbar a:hover {
    color: #00bcd4; /* Accent color */
}

/* Mobile Menu Button (Hidden on Desktop) */
.menu-toggle {
    display: none;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
}

/* Sections */
section {
    padding: 60px 5%;
    min-height: 40vh;
}

.hero {
    background-color: #e0f7fa;
    text-align: center;
}

/* Project Grid */
#projects {
    background-color: white;
}

.project-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 30px;
}

.project-card {
    background-color: #f4f4f9;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    text-align: center;
}

/* Footer */
footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 15px;
    background-color: #1a1a2e;
    color: white;
}

/* --- Media Query for Mobile Responsiveness --- */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    #navbar {
        display: none; /* Hide nav links by default on small screens */
        flex-direction: column;
        width: 100%;
        position: absolute;
        top: 60px;
        left: 0;
        background-color: #1a1a2e;
    }

    #navbar.active {
        display: flex; /* Show when active */
    }

    #navbar a {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 15px;
        border-top: 1px solid #333;
    }

    .menu-toggle {
        display: block;
    }
}
```

